Competition: Copa Libertadores
Season: 1998
BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/sacups/copa98.html


Round: Preliminary Round

* [Note: for the first time, two Mexican teams were invited to participate in the Copa Libertadores.  América and Guadalajara were chosen; they played a preliminary match to determine who would play as Mexico's first resp. second entrant:

1/15: Club América - Guadalajara                 2-0
          [Ricardo Peláez 7, 30]
       this match has no bearing on the final group table.]

